# Workflow: Setup Component Testing from Scratch

**Routed from:** Master Orchestrator (File 0)
**Use When:** Installing Playwright, creating test-runner config, setting up Wireit targets

## Prerequisites

- ✅ Storybook exists (`.storybook/` configured with `@storybook/web-components-vite`)
- ✅ 44 story files exist in `src/components/`
- ✅ Components use Stencil JS with lit html templates

---

