## Phase 2: Install Dependencies

### Step 2.1: Install Playwright & Test Runner

```
Agent Response:
"Installing Storybook test-runner and Playwright dependencies...

**Dependencies to install:**

- @storybook/test-runner (test execution via Playwright)
- @storybook/addon-interactions (interaction panel in Storybook)
- @axe-core/playwright (accessibility testing)
- axe-playwright (a11y integration)
- jest-image-snapshot (visual regression)

**Note:** @storybook/test is already installed.

**Command:**
```bash
npm install -D @storybook/test-runner @storybook/addon-interactions @axe-core/playwright axe-playwright jest-image-snapshot
```

Should I run this installation? (yes/no)
```

### Step 2.2: Install Playwright Browsers

```bash
npx playwright install
```

