## Phase 4: Add Wireit Targets

### Step 4.1: Update package.json with Wireit test targets

```
Agent Response:
"Adding Wireit test targets to package.json...

**New scripts to add:**

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "test:storybook": "wireit",
    "test:storybook:all": "wireit",
    "test:storybook:update": "wireit"
  },
  "wireit": {
    "test:storybook": {
      "command": "npx test-storybook --url http://localhost:6006 --browsers chromium",
      "dependencies": ["stencil:build"]
    },
    "test:storybook:all": {
      "command": "npx test-storybook --url http://localhost:6006 --browsers chromium firefox webkit",
      "dependencies": ["stencil:build"]
    },
    "test:storybook:update": {
      "command": "npx test-storybook --url http://localhost:6006 --browsers chromium --updateSnapshot",
      "dependencies": ["stencil:build"]
    }
  }
}
```

Should I update package.json? (yes/no)
```

